Subject: [PATCH 2/3] Add internal token authentication for proxy endpoints to
 bypass NextAuth

Introduces a new acceptance token mechanism in `apps/web/lib/acceptance-token.ts` to bypass NextAuth for proxy endpoints (`/api/deployments/[deploymentId]/proxy` and `/[...path]`). The `apps/web/lib/acceptance-checks.ts` utility now automatically includes the `x-internal-acceptance-token` header for proxy URLs. The proxy route handlers in `apps/web/app/api/deployments/[deploymentId]/proxy/route.ts` and `apps/web/app/api/deployments/[deploymentId]/proxy/[...path]/route.ts` are updated to validate this token before applying standard authentication, while still enforcing deployment ownership.

